extends ../../views/layout

block content
  .row
    .col-md-9.col-md-offset-2
      h1.highlight= title
      p Login using one of these services.
      ul.social-list 
        li 
          a(href='/auth/twitter')
            i.fa.fa-twitter-square.fa-3x
        li
          a(href='/auth/github')
            i.fa.fa-github-square.fa-3x
        li
          a(href='/auth/linkedin')
            i.fa.fa-linkedin-square.fa-3x
         li
          a(href='/auth/linkedin')
            i.fa.fa-google-plus-square.fa-3x
      .clearfix
      p Or use form below if you signed up directly through the site.
      form.form-signin(method="post" action="/users/login")
        .form-group
          label Username (use email)
          input.form-control(type="text" name="username")
        .form-group
          label Password
          input.form-control(type="password" name="password")
        .form-group
          button.btn.btn-default Login
      p
        | Would you like to create polls as well as vote in them? You must register for an account, which is fast, free and simple (and EasyPoll never shares or sells user data). Go 
        a(href='/register')  here
        |  to register.
